        <h2>Location Information:</h2>
        <p>You may choose to publish your location in your Hippos and in your Hippo profile. You may also tell us your location when you set your trend location on usehippo.com or your computer or mobile device sends us location information. We may also use other data from your device to determine location, for example, information about wireless networks or cell towers near your mobile device, or your IP address. We may use and store information about your location to provide features of our Services, such as Hubbling with your location, and to improve and customize the Services, for example, with more relevant content like local trends, stories, ads, and suggestions for people to follow. Learn more about Hippo’s use of location here, and how to set your location preferences here.
        </p>
